{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "Workspace",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Workspace",
            "label": "Log Analytics workspace",
            "type": 5,
            "isRequired": true,
            "query": "Resources\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces'\n| project value = id, label = name",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "resourceTypeFilter": {
                "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces": true
              }
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
            "value": ""
          },
          {
            "id": "TimeRange",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "label": "Time range",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 2592000000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                {
                  "durationMs": 604800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2592000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 7776000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 15552000000
                }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            }
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# Azure FinOps & Cost Management Workbook\n\n**Workspace:** `{Workspace:label}`  •  **Range:** `{TimeRange:label}`\n\nCost attribution and trend analysis built on the `CostExport_CL` custom table that the cost-ingestion Logic App populates from the scheduled Cost Management export.\n\n## How to read this\n- **Cost** values are in the export's billing currency (`Currency_s`).\n- Attribution by **Resource Group** and **Tags** drives FinOps accountability — untagged or unattributed spend is highlighted below.\n- If charts are empty, confirm an export has landed in the storage container and the Logic App run succeeded (data lands in `CostExport_CL`)."
      },
      "name": "title"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Summary",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "CostExport_CL\n| summarize Total = round(sum(Cost_d), 2)\n| extend Total = strcat(tostring(Total))",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Total cost (selected range)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "stat",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false
              },
              "statSettings": {
                "valueAggregation": "None",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "type": "static",
                  "mode": "background",
                  "heatmapPalette": "greenRed",
                  "thresholdsGrid": []
                },
                "iconSettings": {
                  "thresholdsGrid": []
                },
                "tagText": "",
                "valueFontStyle": "auto"
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "stat_total_cost"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "CostExport_CL\n| summarize ResourceGroups = dcount(ResourceGroup)",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Resource groups with cost",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "stat",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "stat_rg_count"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "CostExport_CL\n| extend HasOwner = iff(isnotempty(Tags_s) and Tags_s has 'owner', Cost_d, real(null))\n| summarize Attributed = sum(HasOwner), Total = sum(Cost_d)\n| extend UnattributedPct = round(100.0 * (Total - coalesce(Attributed, 0.0)) / iff(Total == 0, 1.0, Total), 1)\n| project UnattributedPct",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Untagged spend (% missing owner)",
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Workspace}"
              ],
              "visualization": "stat",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "stat_untagged_pct"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "summary_group"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| extend Day = todatetime(Date_s)\n| summarize DailyCost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by bin(Day, 1d)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Daily cost trend",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "timechart"
      },
      "name": "chart_daily_trend"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| summarize Cost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by ResourceGroup\n| where Cost > 0\n| order by Cost desc\n| take 15",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Top 15 resource groups by cost",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "barchart"
      },
      "name": "chart_cost_by_rg"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| summarize Cost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by ConsumedService_s\n| where Cost > 0\n| order by Cost desc\n| take 15",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Cost by service",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "barchart"
      },
      "name": "chart_cost_by_service"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| summarize Cost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by SubscriptionName_s\n| where Cost > 0\n| order by Cost desc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Cost by subscription",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "piechart"
      },
      "name": "chart_cost_by_subscription"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## Tag attribution\n\nSpend grouped by the `owner` tag value parsed from the export's `Tags_s` column. Rows where the owner tag is absent surface as **(untagged)** — these are the FinOps backlog."
      },
      "name": "tag_section_header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| extend Owner = extract('\"owner\"\\\\s*:\\\\s*\"([^\"]*)\"', 1, tolower(Tags_s))\n| extend Owner = iff(isempty(Owner), '(untagged)', Owner)\n| summarize Cost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by Owner\n| where Cost > 0\n| order by Cost desc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Cost by owner tag",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "piechart",
        "gridSettings": {
          "formatters": [
            {
              "columnMatch": "Cost",
              "formatter": 8,
              "formatOptions": {
                "palette": "blue"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "50",
      "name": "table_cost_by_owner"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| extend CostCenter = extract('\"costcenter\"\\\\s*:\\\\s*\"([^\"]*)\"', 1, tolower(Tags_s))\n| extend CostCenter = iff(isempty(CostCenter), '(untagged)', CostCenter)\n| summarize Cost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by CostCenter\n| where Cost > 0\n| order by Cost desc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Cost by costCenter tag",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "piechart",
        "gridSettings": {
          "formatters": [
            {
              "columnMatch": "Cost",
              "formatter": 8,
              "formatOptions": {
                "palette": "green"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "50",
      "name": "table_cost_by_costcenter"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## Top resources\n\nHighest-cost individual resources in the selected range. Use this to spot anomalies and untagged high-spend resources."
      },
      "name": "resource_section_header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "CostExport_CL\n| summarize Cost = round(sum(Cost_d), 2) by ResourceId, ResourceGroup, ConsumedService_s\n| where Cost > 0\n| order by Cost desc\n| take 25",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Top 25 resources by cost",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Workspace}"
        ],
        "visualization": "table",
        "gridSettings": {
          "formatters": [
            {
              "columnMatch": "Cost",
              "formatter": 8,
              "formatOptions": {
                "palette": "red"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "sortBy": []
      },
      "name": "table_top_resources"
    }
  ],
  "fallbackResourceIds": [
    "azure monitor"
  ],
  "$schema": "https://github.com/Microsoft/Application-Insights-Workbooks/blob/master/schema/workbook.json"
}